OL,3,CStourbridge park visitors told to not
OL,4,Cbe alarmed as pool water turns blue
OL,6,FVisitors to Mary Stevens Park in
OL,7,FStourbridge are being told to not be
OL,8,Falarmed about the pools' water
OL,9,Fappearing a turquoise blue colour.
OL,11,FThe warm weather has been blamed for
OL,12,Fthe growth of algae which reduces
OL,13,Foxygen levels in the water.
OL,15,FSpecialists have been treating the
OL,16,Fpool in the hope of saving the lives
OL,17,Fof thousands of fish.
OL,19,FThe blue colour should reflect more of
OL,20,Fthe sunlight and improve the levels of
OL,21,Foxygen.
