OL,3,CStourbridge park visitors told to not
OL,4,Cbe alarmed as pool water turns blue
OL,6,FDudley Metropolitan Borough Council,
OL,7,FCllr Damian Corfield
OL,8,Fsaid:"Exceptionally sunny and warm
OL,9,Fperiods result in sunlight penetrating
OL,10,Fthe water and increasing algae growth.
OL,12,F"Algae reduces oxygen levels in the
OL,13,Fpool and can be harmful to fish and
OL,14,Fgeneral water quality, so we have had
OL,15,Fto take action.
OL,17,F"Visitors to the park will notice the
OL,18,Fpool to have a blue appearance, but I
OL,19,Fwould urge them not to be alarmed by
OL,20,Fthis.
