OL,4,Cbe alarmed as pool water turns blue
OL,6,F"It is part of our treatment plan to
OL,7,Freflect the sun, reduce algae and
OL,8,Fimprove the oxygen within the pool. We
OL,9,Fhave also deployed an additional pump
OL,10,Fto compliment the work of the central
OL,11,Ffountain to improve oxygen levels."
